Definition: any of numerous plants of the genus Begonia grown for their attractive glossy asymmetrical leaves and colorful flowers in usually terminal cymes or racemes
Synonyms: flower, genus_Begonia, m, any, of, numerous, plants, the, genus, Begonia, grown, for, their, attractive, glossy, asymmetrical, leaves, and, colorful, flowers, in, usually, terminal, cymes, or, racemes
Category: noun.plant
